        236.45,
        140.6,
        376.82,
        149.6
      ],
      "text": "Datum 6-10-2015",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "page": 4,
      "bbox": [
        236.45,
        163.16,
        343.22,
        172.16
      ],
      "text": "Versie 1.0",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "page": 4,
      "bbox": [
        236.45,
        185.72,
        287.73,
        194.72
      ],
      "text": "Document",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "page": 4,
      "bbox": [
        239.81,
        253.62,
        273.76,
        259.62
      ],
      "text": "2015, UWV",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 4,
      "bbox": [
        232.85,
        253.68,
        237.59,
        259.68
      ],
      "text": "",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 4,
      "bbox": [
        232.85,
        272.01,
        517.49,
        278.01
      ],
      "text": "Alle rechten voorbehouden. Niets uit deze uitgave mag worden verveelvoudigd, opgeslagen in",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 4,
      "bbox": [
        232.85,
        280.53,
        514.02,
        286.53
      ],
      "text": "een geautomatiseerd gegevensbestand, of openbaar gemaakt, in enige vorm, of enige wijze,",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 4,
      "bbox": [
        232.85,
        288.93,
        512.22,
        294.93
      ],
      "text": "hetzij elektronisch, mechanisch, door fotokopieën, opnamen of enige andere manier, zonder",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 4,
      "bbox": [
        232.85,
        297.45,
        384.31,
        303.45
      ],
      "text": "voorafgaande schriftelijke toestemming van UWV.",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
